snippet.title: Introducing the Hobie Mirage Compass (Fishing Edition)
snippet.description:
All new from Hobie, the Mirage Compass.
 
Uncomplicated excellence gives you the ultimate fish hunter. Outfitted with the time-tested MirageDrive with Glide Technology, the Mirage Compass will have you cutting through the water in no time. A stealthy new hull design brings speed while the oversized cockpit allows for maximum stability and a flat deck for standing.
 
Learn more: https://www.hobie.com/kayaks/mirage-compass/
